#MEM id=shared source=/root/yvon/agent-department/shared/README.md
M|shared|This directory contains skills and brand profiles that are shared across all YVON agents. Instead of duplicating these files in every agt's `skills/` folder, all agents reference the files here.
M|shared|```
M|shared|shared/
M|shared|в”њв”Ђв”Ђ skills/
M|shared|в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ agents/        # agt-agnostic skills
