M|shared|в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ coding/        # Coding guidelines
M|shared|в”‚       в””в”Ђв”Ђ 01-karpathy.md
M|shared|в””в”Ђв”Ђ brands/            # Brand profiles
M|shared|в”њв”Ђв”Ђ novizio.md
M|shared|в””в”Ђв”Ђ hourbour.md
M|shared|```
M|shared|Critical вЂ” loaded by all agents. Contains:
M|shared|- ses Start Protocol (required reading order)
M|shared|- Active ses Control (brand isolation rules)
M|shared|- ses End Protocol (logging requirements)
M|shared|- Token budget guidelines
M|shared|Critical вЂ” loaded by all agents. Contains:
M|shared|- Think Before Coding guidelines
M|shared|- Simplicity First principles
M|shared|- Surgical Changes rules
M|shared|- Goal-Driven Execution methodology
M|shared|Brand profile for Novizio (fashion e-commerce).
M|shared|- Identity, ICP, brand voice
M|shared|- Platform CTAs, cnt pillars
M|shared|- agt-specific notes
M|shared|Brand profile for Hourbour (fintech SaaS).
M|shared|- Identity, ICP, brand voice
M|shared|- Platform CTAs, cnt pillars
M|shared|- agt-specific notes
M|shared|**Rule:** Edit ONLY the files in this directory. Do NOT edit the stub files in individual agt folders.
M|shared|When you update a shared skill:
M|shared|1. Edit the file in `shared/`
M|shared|2. The individual agt stub files redirect to the shared version
M|shared|3. After editing, run `scripts/skills-sync.sh` to verify consistency
M|shared|Individual agt `skills/` folders may still contain copies of shared skills with a `deprecated: true` frontmatter and a `redirect` field pointing here. These are stubs for backward compatibility during